=\"#000000\"><label for=\"qsintdefsvolume\">Vol:</label>&nbsp;</font></th>\n                          <td><input type=\"text\" name=\"volume\" id=\"qsintdefsvolume\" size=\"4\" maxlength=\"10\" value=\"\" style=\"font-family:verdana,arial,helvetica;font-size:10px;\"></td>\n                          <th><font size=\"-2\" face=\"verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif\" color=\"#000000\"><label for=\"qsintdefsfirstpage\">Page:</label>&nbsp;</font></th>\n                          <td><input type=\"text\" name=\"firstpage\" id=\"qsintdefsfirstpage\" size=\"4\" maxlength=\"10\" value=\"\" style=\"font-family:verdana,arial,helvetica;font-size:10px;\"></td>\n                        </tr>\n                      </tbody></table>\n                    </td>\n                    <td bgcolor=\"#DBDBDB\"><img alt=\" \" width=\"2\" height=\"2\" src=\"/icons/spacer.gif\"></td>\n                  </tr>\n                </tbody></table>\n              </form>\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n        </tbody></table>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td colspan=\"3\">\n        <img alt=\" \" width=\"2\" height=\"2\" src=\"/icons/spacer.gif\"><br>\n        <font size=\"-2\" face=\"verdana,arial,helvetica\"></font>\n        <hr align=\"left\" size=\"1\" color=\"#000000\" noshade=\"\">\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody></table>\n  <h2>About <i>Microbiology</i></h2>\n  <h3>ISSNs: 1350-0872 (Print); 1465-2080 (Online)</h3>\n  <p><i>Microbiology</i> (formerly <i>Journal of General Microbiology</i>) is one of the world’s leading microbiological journals. For over 60 years it has been publishing high-quality research across the whole spectrum of the subject. <i>Microbiology</i> is published by the , a learned society that promotes microbiology at all levels.</p>\n  <p>Features of <i>Microbiology</i> include:</p>\n  <ul>\n    <li>Wide-ranging and rigorously peer-reviewed research papers and <a href=\"/mic/misc/ifora.shtml#reviews\">reviews</a>\n    </li>\n    <li>User-friendly <a href=\"/mic/misc/subonline.shtml\">online submission</a> and peer review\n    </li>\n    <li>\n      <a href=\"/mic/papbyrecent.dtl\">Papers in Press</a>- advance online publication of manuscripts accepted for publication in <i>Microbiology</i>\n    </li>\n    <li>A <a href=\"/mic/misc/ifora.shtml#Microbiology%20Comment\"><i>Microbiology</i> Comment</a> section for responses from readers on articles published in the journal\n    </li>\n    <li>Occasional special issues focusing on subjects of particular interest</li>\n    <li>An international <a href=\"/mic/misc/edboard.shtml\">Editorial Board</a> with expertise across the whole of microbiology\n    </li>\n    <li>Over 3000 pages published per annual volume</li>\n    <li>Excellent editorial and production standards</li>\n    <li>No page or colour figure charges</li>\n    <li>Authors receive 25 free reprints of their paper</li>\n  </ul>\n  <ul>\n    <li>\n      <a href=\"/mic/misc/self_archiving.dtl\">Self-archiving</a>. Details of the SGM policy on author self-archiving\n    </li>\n    <li>\n      <a href=\"/mic/misc/open_option.dtl\">Paid immediate open access</a>. Details of the SGM Open Option scheme that allows immediate open access to articles\n    </li>\n  </ul>\n  <hr>\n  <h3>Submission of papers</h3>\n  <p>Papers for publication must be submitted via the internet using our <a href=\"/mic/misc/subonline.shtml\">online submission system</a>. See the <a href=\"/mic/misc/ifora.shtml\">Instructions for Authors</a> for more information.</p>\n  <hr>\n  <table width=\"60%\" border=\"3\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"4\" bgcolor=\"#99CCFF\">\n    <tbody><tr>\n      <td><b>: 3.025.</b><br>\n      <br>\n      Ranked <b><font color=\"#0000CC\">9th</font></b> in the microbiology category by the (<b>0.04951</b>).<br>\n      <br>\n      More than <b>11,000 citations</b>, making it the <b><font color=\"#0000CC\">10th</font></b> most highly cited microbiology journal.</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody></table><br>\n  <hr>\n  <h3><i>Microbiology</i> Editorial Office</h3>\n  <p>Permission requests should be sent to <span id=\"em0\">micro.permission{at}sgm.ac.uk</span>\n   (Editorial Assistant) at the Editorial Office.</p>\n  <p>All other enquiries should be directed to <span id=\"em1\">r.walker{at}sgm.ac.uk</span>\n   (Senior Staff Editor) at the Editorial Office.</p>\n  <p><i>Microbiology</i> Editorial Office<br>\n  Society for General Microbiology<br>\n  Marlborough House<br>\n  Basingstoke Road<br>\n  Spencers Wood<br>\n  Reading RG7 1AG<br>\n  UK<br>\n  <b>e-mail:</b> <span id=\"em2\">micro{at}sgm.ac.uk</span>\n  <br>\n  <b>Phone:</b> +44 (0)118 9881804 <b>Fax:</b> +44 (0)118 9881834</p>Editorial staff: Rachel Walker (Senior Staff Editor), Chris Sinclair, Ian Atherton and Stefan Sidorowicz (Staff Editors), and Kendra Waite (Editorial Assistant).<br>\n  <hr>\n  <p>Last updated 6 December 2010</p>\n  <p></p>\n  <hr noshade=\"\" align=\"left\" width=\"450\">\n  <table cellpadding=\"2\" cellspacing=\"2\" width=\"450\">\n    <tbody><tr>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/mic/\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">HOME</font></a>\n      </td>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/mic/help/\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">HELP</font></a>\n      </td>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/mic/cgi/feedback\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">FEEDBACK</font></a>\n      </td>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/mic/subscriptions\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">SUBSCRIPTIONS</font></a>\n      </td>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/mic/contents-by-date.0.shtml\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">ARCHIVE</font></a>\n      </td>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/mic/search.dtl\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">SEARCH</font></a>\n      </td>\n      <td width=\"75\" nowrap=\"\"></td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody></table>\n  <table cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"2\" width=\"375\">\n    <tbody><tr>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/ijs/\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">INT J SYST EVOL MICROBIOL</font></a>\n      </td>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#E1E1E1\" nowrap=\"\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#000000\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">MICROBIOLOGY</font></td>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/vir/\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">J GEN VIROL</font></a>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/jmm/\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">J MED MICROBIOL</font></a>\n      </td>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\" colspan=\"2\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">ALL SGM JOURNALS</font></a>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody></table><font size=\"-1\"><strong><a target=\"_top\" href=\"/mic/misc/te